        {
            "title": "自願醫保｜奪命流感爆發 自願醫保有無得保？",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"流感威脅再升溫下，一旦不幸中招要入院，自願醫保又幫到幾多醫藥費？g\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8DCxrZyiJMPIYpDHexkwcw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-05/cef3dcc0-37b2-11f0-95fa-e14bac50b88b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">流感威脅再升溫下，一旦不幸中招要入院，自願醫保又幫到幾多醫藥費？g</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">捱過冬天後以後可以告別流感，但衞生防護中心提醒季節性流感活躍程度回升，尤其是乙型流感。兩大港人熱門旅遊點台灣及日本，前者有奪命流感H3N2爆發，單周9萬宗確診個案及6人死亡；日本繼甲型流感肆虐後，現在又到乙型流感接力，單周流感確診人數破11萬，九成屬於乙型流感。流感威脅再升溫下，一旦不幸中招要入院，自願醫保又幫到幾多醫藥費？</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://yhoo.it/3GLNxtA\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">下載Yahoo財經APP</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</strong></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">原來門診都有得保 只要符合一個條件</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近年幾乎每季都有流感警示，大家聽得多，有感冒時都會擔心是否中了流感。雖然流感病徵與一般感冒相似，醫生一般會經三種檢查方式，診斷病人是否確診流感。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-1e89356e-0329-42e2-b435-3f0718bbc0f3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">首先是臨床診斷，醫生按發高燒、乾咳、肌肉痠痛等作初步診斷。接著是快速測試，像疫情時大家熟悉的測試程序般，由棉棒擦拭鼻腔或咽喉抽取樣本，一般 15 至 30 分鐘內就會有結果。現時市場上不少快速測試包，都包括了快速測試流感功能。最後是核酸測試檢測病毒物質，準確度相當高不過收費較貴。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><blockquote class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull\" style=\"padding-bottom:min(300px, undefined%)\"></div></blockquote><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"經醫生診斷需要入院，不論是購買標準或靈活計劃自願醫保，該次門診及出院後跟進門診，都獲納入受保範圍之內。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/QjkZHGubuUJgpygmgmz4eQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-03/a0187010-9f57-11ec-bf77-8e507ffb3cb8\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">經醫生診斷需要入院，不論是購買標準或靈活計劃自願醫保，該次門診及出院後跟進門診，都獲納入受保範圍之內。</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">現時到私家醫院進行流感相關檢查，收費由四百多元至1,200元不等。即使流感中招，門診檢查一般都不在自願醫保保障範圍內。因為流感中招都未必需要入院，病情較輕可服用退燒藥、止咳及收鼻水藥治療，病情較重則需要服用抗病毒藥物，甚至入院吊鹽水、接收氧氣治療。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">假如經醫生診斷需要入院，不論是購買標準或靈活計劃自願醫保，受惠「入院前或出院後／日間手術前後的門診護理 」保障項目，該次門診及出院後跟進門診，都獲納入受保範圍之內，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:部分靈活計劃;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.hangseng.com/zh-hk/personal/insurance-mpf/medical-critical-illness/vhis/flexi/?_gl=1*bo1anu*_gcl_aw*R0NMLjE3NjkxNTY2MTQuQ2owS0NRaUExY3pMQmhEaEFSSXNBSUVjN3VpbHE3eVBEMkxtUjJJNjFSWTh2djBuNjFIUm9HQUFVWHFuTk5XYldSamU3VzBxS0NOT2xtTWFBZ2hRRUFMd193Y0I.*_gcl_dc*R0NMLjE3NzI3MTU4OTEuQ05ldm1xSHBpSk1ERlZkNjlRY2RVWWNLd1E.*_gcl_au*MTkxMDc3NzA3My4xNzY5OTM1NTY5\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">部分靈活計劃</a>更提供30日內門診全數賠償的醫療保障。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">流感高峰期 享求醫「捷徑」優惠</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當局不時警告流感高峰期來襲，原因係提醒大家保重身體，避免市民迫爆公立醫院急症室，減輕公共醫療壓力。以往當流感高峰期再遇上長假期時，急症室等候6至8小時是等閒事，如不幸這段期間中招，想轉用「捷徑」到私家醫院睇急症，自願醫保就可以幫到手。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"預早購買自願醫保靈活計劃，由半私家房至私家房，膳食、主診醫生巡房費及雜項開支都獲得保障。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hz__jsM3V4eM0F_vGfkN3w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/d54f1700-1895-11f1-bf9a-950cbc1dc0b8\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">預早購買自願醫保靈活計劃，由半私家房至私家房，膳食、主診醫生巡房費及雜項開支都獲得保障。</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">私家醫院樣樣都計錢，先講病房，普通病房每日收費由850元至1900元，半私家病房每日收費更加碼至1050元至3800元，再加上膳食、主診醫生巡房費及雜項開支，還有專科醫生費，自費的話醫一次流感可能至少相當於一個月人工。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">預早購買<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:自願醫保靈活計劃;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.hangseng.com/zh-hk/personal/insurance-mpf/medical-critical-illness/vhis/flexi/?_gl=1*bo1anu*_gcl_aw*R0NMLjE3NjkxNTY2MTQuQ2owS0NRaUExY3pMQmhEaEFSSXNBSUVjN3VpbHE3eVBEMkxtUjJJNjFSWTh2djBuNjFIUm9HQUFVWHFuTk5XYldSamU3VzBxS0NOT2xtTWFBZ2hRRUFMd193Y0I.*_gcl_dc*R0NMLjE3NzI3MTU4OTEuQ05ldm1xSHBpSk1ERlZkNjlRY2RVWWNLd1E.*_gcl_au*MTkxMDc3NzA3My4xNzY5OTM1NTY5\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">自願醫保靈活計劃</a>，由半私家房至私家房，膳食、主診醫生巡房費及雜項開支都獲得保障，部分計劃更提供使用醫療卡免找數保障，使用私家醫院治療流感重症，心理及財務壓力都大減。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">出門旅行，都可能會擔心旅途上患上流感。一般旅遊保險都提供海外醫療費用、回港後續治療費用、住院津貼等保障，但申請理賠須提交診斷證明書（最好少英文版）、醫療費用收據、處方藥物證明。部分自願醫保靈活計劃亦提供海外保障，由大中華、亞洲甚至全球，投保人可按需要選擇計劃級別，計劃會為受保人支付住院及手術費用，不設細項賠償限額。如不時出門公幹及旅遊，購買較高階的<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:靈活計劃;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.hangseng.com/zh-hk/personal/insurance-mpf/medical-critical-illness/vhis/flexi/?_gl=1*bo1anu*_gcl_aw*R0NMLjE3NjkxNTY2MTQuQ2owS0NRaUExY3pMQmhEaEFSSXNBSUVjN3VpbHE3eVBEMkxtUjJJNjFSWTh2djBuNjFIUm9HQUFVWHFuTk5XYldSamU3VzBxS0NOT2xtTWFBZ2hRRUFMd193Y0I.*_gcl_dc*R0NMLjE3NzI3MTU4OTEuQ05ldm1xSHBpSk1ERlZkNjlRY2RVWWNLd1E.*_gcl_au*MTkxMDc3NzA3My4xNzY5OTM1NTY5\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">靈活計劃</a>，應對流感威脅就多一重保障。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%87%AA%E9%A1%98%E9%86%AB%E4%BF%9D%EF%BD%9C%E5%A5%AA%E5%91%BD%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC-%E8%87%AA%E9%A1%98%E9%86%AB%E4%BF%9D%E6%9C%89%E7%84%A1%E5%BE%97%E4%BF%9D%EF%BC%9F-232456731.html",
