lm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CAT/\">Caterpillar</a>(CAT.US)挫3.5%。銀行股<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:11;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:摩通;cpos:11;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/JPM/\">摩通</a>(JPM.US)、摩根士丹利(MS.US)跌2%至3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:12;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:甲骨文;cpos:12;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/ORCL/\">甲骨文</a>(ORCL.US)計劃裁減數千名員工，以應對大規模人工智能數據中心擴張帶來的資金短缺而採取的措施之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:13;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Costco;cpos:13;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/COST/\">Costco</a>(COST.US)收市後公布業績，第二財季每股盈利4.58美元，略高於預期的4.55美元；收入為696億美元，高於預期的693億美元。 經調整同店銷售額按年增長6.7%，預期增長為6.3%。盤後Costco微跌。</p></div>",
